//! Emit MLIR from a resolved HIR chunk.
//!
//! Produces an MLIR `Module` using standard dialects (`arith`, `func`, `llvm`).
//! All statements run in `func.func @main`. Locals are stack slots created
//! with `llvm.alloca` at function entry.

